com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.venues

Class VenueRequestExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.RequestExecutor<Venue>
      • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.venues.VenueRequestExecutor

  • public class VenueRequestExecutor
extends RequestExecutor<Venue>
    Request executor provided by VenuesApi. Use this class if you want to get single venue through fluent API in chained fashion, for instance: 
       
   IKontaktCloud kontaktCloud = KontaktCloud.newInstance();
   Venue venue = kontaktCloud.venues().fetch(ID).execute();
